SET Zoom TO 1
SET MeetingNo TO 0
IF (System.ProcessIsNotRunning ProcessName: $'''CptHost''') THEN
    LOOP WHILE (Zoom) < (2)
        Clipboard.GetText Text=> ClipboardText
        WebAutomation.LaunchEdge Url: ClipboardText WindowState: WebAutomation.BrowserWindowState.Normal ClearCache: False ClearCookies: False Timeout: 60 BrowserInstance=> Browser
        WebAutomation.CloseWebBrowser BrowserInstance: Browser
        IF (UIAutomation.Windows.IsFocusedByTitleClass Title: $'''Zoom''' Class: $'''ZPPTMainFrmWndClassEx''') THEN
            UIAutomation.Windows.CloseByTitleClass Title: $'''Zoom''' Class: $'''ZPPTMainFrmWndClassEx'''
        END
        WAIT (System.ProcessToStart ProcessName: $'''CptHost''') FOR 300 
                ON ERROR TimeoutError
                    SET Zoom TO 2
                    GOTO SirAbsent
                END
        Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: MeetingNo IncrementValue: 1 IncreasedValue=> MeetingNo
        WAIT (System.ProcessToStop ProcessName: $'''CptHost''')
        WAIT 3
        WAIT (System.ProcessToStop ProcessName: $'''CptHost''')
        IF (UIAutomation.Windows.IsNotOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''''' Class: $'''ZPUnlimitedGroupMeetingClass''') THEN
        ELSE
            UIAutomation.Windows.Close Window: appmask['Window \'Zoom\' 2']
        END
        LABEL SirAbsent
    END
ELSE
    System.TerminateProcessByName ProcessName: $'''Zoom'''
END
